data.name: battleships-web
data.description: Web-based Battleships game, featuring a front-end interface built with React and a back-end server for managing game logic and storing player data, built using Spring and JPA.

data.name: battleships-mobile
data.description: Android Battleships game built using Kotlin and Jetpack Compose. The game serves as a client application for the API developed in the "battlehips-web" project, utilizing RESTful API calls to communicate with the back-end server.

data.description: The Sports API allows the user to perform creation and management of users, sports, routes and activities.
